To be fair, though, we rocked the headband look.

502
00:21:22,481 --> 00:21:23,947
哈  哈  有趣
Ha ha fun fun.

503
00:21:23,949 --> 00:21:26,950
玛蒂  你 17 岁之前不允许考驾照
Maddie, no license till you're 17.

504
00:21:26,952 --> 00:21:28,952
看你这个造型怎么拗
Rock that look.

505
00:21:28,954 --> 00:21:32,356
17 岁  真的
17?! Seriously?

506
00:21:32,358 --> 00:21:33,557
莫非你想等到 18 岁再说
You want to make it 18?

507
00:21:33,559 --> 00:21:35,659
啊  17 岁啊  等不及了
Ah, 17. Looking forward to it.

508
00:21:35,661 --> 00:21:37,795
还有  丽芙
And Liv,

509
00:21:37,797 --> 00:21:39,429
既然你这么喜欢开车
since you like driving so much,

510
