just to get the newspaper.

515
00:21:51,911 --> 00:21:53,811
我不知道你们怎么看
I don't know.

516
00:21:54,946 --> 00:21:56,480
没错  孩子们
That's right, girls.

517
00:21:56,482 --> 00:21:58,749
