亚蒂的狼尾巴
One of Artie's wolf tails. Yeah.

541
00:23:04,616 --> 00:23:07,618
哦  还有  你今年舞会有舞伴了
Oh! Also I got you a date to the prom.

542
00:23:07,620 --> 00:23:09,987
对哦
Yeah.

543
